# Claude Code
.claude/worktree-bypass

# Beads / Dolt files
# Pearl Dolt stores live at .smooth/dolt/ and are NOT git-tracked.
# Sync is via dolt's own `refs/dolt/data` ref (push/pull) — the same
# pattern beads uses (`.beads/embeddeddolt/` ignored, sync via
# `bd dolt push`/`pull`). Pearl th-975dfe (2026-06-13) flipped this
# repo off the old "track noms binaries in git" model that produced
# recurring merge conflicts when main moved forward while a feature
# worktree was open. Fresh clones bootstrap their store via
# `th pearls init` which clones from origin's refs/dolt/data.
/.dolt/
.smooth/dolt/
.beads-credential-key
.smooth/pearls.db
.smooth/pearls.db-wal
.smooth/pearls.db-shm
.archivist-diag.txt
